snippet.title: Surface Area - MathHelp.com - Math Help
snippet.description: For a complete lesson on surface area, go to http://www.MathHelp.com - 1000+ online math lessons featuring a personal math teacher inside every lesson! In this lesson, students learn that the surface area of a 3-dimensional figure is the sum of the areas of all the faces of the figure. Students are then asked to find the surface area of prisms and pyramids.
